definition.zh_def: 一種心理學理論，強調個體的無意識和集體無意識的作用。
definition.en_def: A psychological theory emphasizing the role of the unconscious and collective unconscious in individuals.
definition.example: Carl Jung's theories have greatly influenced modern psychology.
